{"tid":1946280,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"零距離科學: 大麻兩面睇","createTime":"2020-03-27T13:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T15:00:27.000Z","uid":35070,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2897bc6097d4ff21feea45fe5a4ac39cb3b488c9","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"大麻兩面睇<br />\n大麻是世上其中一種最古老和最具爭議性的藥物，而這種藥物現正面臨一個非常特別的時刻。攝製團隊調查了最新的醫學和科學研究，找出大麻對大腦和人體的影響。<br />\n<br />\n自2018年11月1日起，醫學用大麻在英國正式合法化，不過在實際上仍然存在很多爭議。急症室醫生賈偉德．阿卜杜莫尼希望找出大麻是否對病人有利，還是會帶來傷害。"},{"pid":"3d01f1880fc2737087d7de9341ef45f9bb4a3bac","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bffe65d4837741cec9385583a36a3f6a582f6a","tid":1946280,"uid":237497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"有冇lsd"},{"pid":"68153eb0634b85cf5a0738eb97e1440090bdeffe","tid":1946280,"uid":3987,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f640cbc721161a5e78794a8329406d24093c207f","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"79bffe65d4837741cec9385583a36a3f6a582f6a","tid":1946280,"uid":237497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"有冇lsd"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"醫藥用大麻應該得好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd7bd59818054f5bddb6c0356c21471d97df44a","tid":1946280,"uid":53922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"又係一個高質RTHK 31節目"},{"pid":"71eae8c0a60c6847330f3bf9eea9f789c9e7ae27","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7bd7bd59818054f5bddb6c0356c21471d97df44a","tid":1946280,"uid":53922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"又係一個高質RTHK 31節目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:07.000Z","msg":"大麻二酚（Cannabidiol，CBD）是大麻百多隻有效成分中最具醫療價值的一種，有保護神經、改善皮膚發炎、抗氧化、舒緩皮膚敏感泛紅、為皮膚表層建立保護屏障、改善皮膚自我修復力；對恢復皮膚健康、舒緩皮膚問題的能力，可以治療濕疹等病。<br />\n<br />\n四氫大麻酚（Tetrahydrocannabinol，簡稱THC），又稱&Delta;9-四氫大麻酚（&Delta;9-THC）、&Delta;1-THC（根據舊命名法），為大麻素之一，是大麻中的主要精神活性物質。"},{"pid":"c2f4b6b8928996937ace94d93e79a66f521af3fb","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7bd7bd59818054f5bddb6c0356c21471d97df44a","tid":1946280,"uid":53922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"又係一個高質RTHK 31節目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"香港應該無其他電視台夠膽播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6819085dec8297703d9d365669273f69457098d","tid":1946280,"uid":30294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2f4b6b8928996937ace94d93e79a66f521af3fb","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7bd7bd59818054f5bddb6c0356c21471d97df44a","tid":1946280,"uid":53922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"又係一個高質RTHK 31節目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"香港應該無其他電視台夠膽播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"但(醫療用)大麻合法化依家已經成為好普遍既議題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b37b53cb36f9e01b823d623f03e01a05b057d01","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64b97f0047314ccc3d9725ea9136deeb237bc95","tid":1946280,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"有無外國巴絲試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />